ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/chen-jin-dong-31" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$chen-jin-dong-31'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c6531d73764db086e1acec3de8526944_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="陈晋东"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/jingshenjiankang/chen-jin-dong-31/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/chen-jin-dong-31" data-hovercard='p$t$chen-jin-dong-31'>陈晋东</a><div class="bio">精神卫生研究</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/beebuzz" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$beebuzz'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5613c29c9bc3dc08da27214ae80a1419_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="陈雪峰"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/jingshenjiankang/beebuzz/answers" class="answers text-muted">5 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/beebuzz" data-hovercard='p$t$beebuzz'>陈雪峰</a><div class="bio">心理学博士</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/zan-ju-6" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$zan-ju-6'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0247174e488afe4ed4ad2f94fe93f40e_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="陈祉妍"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/jingshenjiankang/zan-ju-6/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/zan-ju-6" data-hovercard='p$t$zan-ju-6'>陈祉妍</a><div class="bio">中国科学院心理研究所 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 教授</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/fan-fu-min-34" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$fan-fu-min-34'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d768007379f6fc8276c2efe3f41b6e64_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="樊富珉"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/jingshenjiankang/